# Spark Social - Project Overview

This is a Flutter application for a social media platform inspired by TikTok, integrated with the Bluesky/AT Protocol.

## Main Entry Points
- [lib/main.dart](mdc:lib/main.dart) - Main application entry point
- [pubspec.yaml](mdc:pubspec.yaml) - Project dependencies and configuration

## Project Structure
- `/lib` - Contains all the Dart code for the application
  - `/src` - New feature-first architecture the project is currently being migrated to
  - `/screens` - UI screens/pages
  - `/services` - Business logic and API integrations
  - `/models` - Data models
  - `/widgets` - Reusable UI components
  - `/utils` - Utility functions and constants
  - `/config` - Configuration files
  - `main.dart` - Main entry point

